# try_phoenix

```elixir
# Define inputs and controls
content_input = Kino.Input.text("Diary Content")
date_input = Kino.Input.date("Date", default: Date.utc_today())

# Buttons belong to the Kino.Control module
submit_button = Kino.Control.button("Save Entry")

# Render them in a grid layout
Kino.Layout.grid([content_input, date_input, submit_button], columns: 1)

```

